    "description": "Ureru Net Advertising Group Co.,Ltd. engages in the advertising business in Japan. It operates in three segments: Digital Marketing Support Business, D2C Business, and Global Information and Communications Business. The company offers online shopping support cloud services, including internet advertising consultation and design, landing page creation, application forms, smartphone and PC servers solutions, and follow-up email and SMS distribution, as well as cross-border e-commerce support and merger and acquisition support. It is also involved in the D2C businesses, such as cosmetics, sanitary products, and health and functional foods; B2B specialized communications equipment rental business; and provision of network applications that allow users to share and access media information. The company was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Fukuoka City, Japan."
